data.description: Welcome to your ideal sanctuary nestled within the tranquil Raindance community! Located conveniently across from Ebenezer Elementary and Middle School, this idyllic location offers the perfect blend of suburban convenience and rural tranquility. Step through the doors of this meticulously crafted 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom haven, spanning over 3,100 square feet, and instantly feel at ease. With a single devoted owner, this residence exudes care and attention to detail. Recent upgrades including a wired security system, solar panels equipped with a battery pack that can charge your vehicle, and a privacy fence, enhance both security and sustainability. What truly distinguishes this home are its generously sized rooms, providing ample space for families to thrive and grow. Low HOA fees ensure affordability, while the proximity to urban amenities ensures convenience without sacrificing serenity. Discover the perfect balance of peaceful countryside living and modern comfort.
